{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一回\"一剑飞雪\"。三个仰慕小李飞刀的年轻江湖人途经破败的探花府，感叹李家后继无人。李坏在铁银衣陪同下回到李家祖宅，面对生父李曼青。曼青先生向李坏坦白了两件终生悔恨之事：一是当年不顾上官家血仇与李坏母亲相恋又遗弃了他们母子；二是二十年前趁薛青碧积劳内伤之际求战并将其击败致死。如今薛青碧后人寄来战书，要以飞刀复仇。曼青先生年老体衰已无胜算，要求李坏替他接战并只许胜不许败。李坏愤怒拒绝，痛斥父亲当年的遗弃。此时银白狐裘妇人拦住李坏，引出同父异母的兄长李正。李正自述十四岁时自以为练成飞刀遍战高手，结果被人切断六指，无法再战。本章揭示了李家两代人的恩怨纠葛与飞刀传承的沉重代价。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_nian_qing_de_jiang_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "最年轻的江湖人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里真的就是小李探花的探花府？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_chen_de_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "深沉的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的，这里就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_nian_qing_de_jiang_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "最年轻的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小李飞刀，例不虚发。我常常恨我自己，恨我为什么没有跟他生在同一个朝代。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_chen_de_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "深沉的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是想和他比一比高下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_nian_qing_de_jiang_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "最年轻的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是，我也不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_nian_qing_de_jiang_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "最年轻的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜李家已经后继无人了，这一代的老庄主李曼青先生虽然有仁有义，而且力图振作，可是小李飞刀的威望，已经不可能在他身上重现了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_nian_qing_de_jiang_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "最年轻的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小李飞刀昔日的雄风，很可能已经不会在任何人身上出现。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_chen_de_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "深沉的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有一件事我一直都想不通。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_nian_qing_de_jiang_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "最年轻的江湖人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_chen_de_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "深沉的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "曼青先生从小就有神童的美名，壮年后为什么会忽然变得消沉了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_chen_de_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "深沉的年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "名侠如名士，总难免风流，你我又何不是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_nian_qing_de_jiang_hu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "最年轻的江湖人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是说，曼青先生的消沉是为了一个女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你不能走，现在你绝不能走。我知道你现在心里在想什么，可是你也应该知道你的父亲现在是多么的需要你，不管怎么样，你总是他亲生的骨肉，是他血中的血，骨中的骨。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你更要知道，要想重振李家的威风，只有靠你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你知不知道你的父亲这次为什么一定要我找你来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yin_yi",
      "text": "我只知道，不管他要我去做什么事我都会去做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "庄主，二少爷回来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你回来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "最近你怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "也没有怎么样，也没有不怎么样。反正我就是这个样子，别人看得惯也好，看不惯也好，反正我也不在乎。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "不在乎？为什么我就不能不在乎？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这是我平生做的第一件错事，因为我明明知道这么做是不可原谅的，是会害人害己的，可是我还要去做。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我扪心自问，永远无法原谅自己的，就是这一点。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "今天我找你来，并不是为了要对你解释这件事，这件事也是永远无法解释的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我生平只做错过两件事，两件事都让我痛苦终生。今天我找你来是为了另外一件事。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "多年前，我初出道急着要表现自己，为了要证明我的声名，并不是靠我祖先的余荫而得来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "那时候，武林中有一位非常成功的人，战无不胜，几乎横扫了武林。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这个人你大概也曾听说过的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我一战而胜举世无双的名剑，当然欣喜若狂。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为后来我才知道，一件我当时所不知道的事情。当时我如果知道这件事，我宁可死也绝不会去求战。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "后来江湖中人都知道这件事，我相信你一定也知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "所以我至今还忘不了他，尤其忘不了他临死前那一瞬间脸上所流露的尊荣。我以前从来没有看过死得那么骄傲的人，我相信以后也永远不会看到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "这是谁写的信，好狂的人！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这个人就是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "是你？怎么会是你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为这封信就和我二十年前写给薛青碧先生的那封信完全一样，除了挑战人的姓名不同之外，别的字句都完全一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这封信，就是薛先生的后人，要来替他父亲复仇，所下的战书。也就是我要付出的代价。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "代价？什么代价？薛家的人凭什么用飞刀来对我们李家的飞刀？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "飞刀，并不是只有李家的人才能练得成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "难道还有别人练成了比我们李家更加可怕的飞刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你现在是不是已经知道这个人是谁了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这就是我要付出的代价。因为我现在的情况，就正如我当年向薛先生挑战时，他的情况一样。我若应战，必败无疑，败就是死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "死并不可怕，可怕的是败。我能死，却不能败。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为我是李家的人，我绝不能败在任何人的飞刀下，我绝不能让我的祖先在九泉下死不瞑目。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "所以我要你回来，要你替我接这一战，要你去为我击败薛家的后代。这一战，你只许生，不许死。只许胜，不许败。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "你的意思难道说是要我去杀了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "是的。到了必要时，你只有杀了他，非杀不可。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "你凭什么要我去做这种事？你凭什么要我去杀一个跟我完全没有仇恨的人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "曼青先生",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为这是李家的事，因为你也是李家的后代。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "直到现在你才承认我是李家的后代，以前呢？以前你为什么不要我们母子两个人？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_man_qing",
      "text": "你的那一位一直在继承李家道统的大少爷呢？他为什么不替你去出头？为什么不去替你杀人？为什么要我去？我为什么要替你去？我……我算是个什么东西了",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_bai_qiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银白狐裘妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "二少爷。你现在还不能走。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_yin_bai_qiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_bai_qiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银白狐裘妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为有个人一定要见你一面，你也非见他一面不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_zheng",
      "text": "是你要见我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "是，是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_zheng",
      "text": "你是谁？为什么一定要见我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "因为我就是刚才你说的那个李家的大儿子。我要见你，只因为我要告诉你，我为什么不能去接这一战。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_zheng",
      "text": "原来你就是李大少爷，我的确很想见你一面，因为我实在也很想问问你，你为什么不能去替李家接这一战。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "我十四岁的时候，就认为自己已经练成了李家天下无敌的飞刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你，也经历过十四岁的阶段，你当然也知道一个年青人在那个阶段中的想法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "等到我知道我那种想法错了的时候，已经太迟了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "那时候，我一心只想替我们李家捞一点能够光宗耀祖的名声，想以我那时自以为已经练成的飞刀，去遍战天下一流高手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_huai",
      "speaker_name": "李坏",
      "listener": "char_li_zheng",
      "text": "你的结果是什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "这就是我的结果，这也是我替我们李家付出的代价。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "李正",
      "listener": "char_li_huai",
      "text": "你呢？现在你是不是也应该为我们李家做一点事了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    }
